This game also has the feature

00:04:12.910 --> 00:04:16.066
that the more effort the other
person--the more the other

00:04:16.066 --> 00:04:18.319
person does--the more you want
to do.

00:04:18.319 --> 00:04:20.720
The more effort your partner
provides into this project the

00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:22.790
more effort you want to provide
in this project.

00:04:22.790 --> 00:04:24.839
I just want to introduce a bit
of jargon here.

00:04:24.839 --> 00:04:28.941
These games in which the more
the other person does the more I

00:04:28.941 --> 00:04:33.110
want to do, these are called
games of strategic complements.

00:04:33.110 --> 00:04:44.149
These are games of strategic
complements.

00:04:44.149 --> 00:04:48.780
So both the investment game and
the game with--the partnership

00:04:48.780 --> 00:04:52.500
firm game are games with
strategic complements.

00:04:52.500 --> 00:04:55.500
We could call the strategies
strategic complements.

00:04:55.500 --> 00:04:59.540
We'll come back to this later
on today.

